Wrong bullet +: Current bullet + is not finished.

original: intros a p q Hcan. unfold minuspf. induction p as [|hd tl IH]. - reflexivity. - destruct q as [|hq tq]. + reflexivity. + simpl. f_equal. apply IH. unfold canonical in Hcan. unfold canonical. apply (proj2 Hcan).
